Summer internship are a great time to build upon your skills.📇
With internship comes outfits.
I feel workwear should be always always fun & interesting… but at the same time it is still important to dress the part professionally & to feel your best.📇
Smart, casual and affordable is our main key elements. 

So even if somedays your work is boring but not your outfit. 

My advice: go out, learn, fail, dream & achieve✨

Swinging Summer; ManyMinis💄
The most daring hemline of the fashion. I call it teeny-tiny skirts. The mini at the moment are more structured, a lil low or high rise, more fitted less flared, and its also about colour’s 
Go appliqued or florals
Go checkers or home school
Go green or shimmy 
All eyes will turn on you. 
A perfect summer blend☀️
